{
  "stem": "22840.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We went up a valley road.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He took us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we joined the partisan group, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- I-- this is something I recall very well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Let me say something about memories.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I have very bad memory, typically.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I don't remember things except technical things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I remember details of-- of technical devices to the iota.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But I have very bad memory generally speaking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I don't remember faces.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I don't remember people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I don't remember names.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I don't remember places.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The time from Banska Bystrica until-- till later, after the war, was always very vivid in my mind, to crystal detail of-- of places and-- and the way a tree would look.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I always wondered if this is my fantasy or if this is truth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And there was no way for me to decide.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Eventually I went back to Slovakia, to court my-- my wife, to chase away the demons, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And what happened is that everything that I recollected was exactly the same I recollected it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Details of stones and trees, different now in some sense, not different in others.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I'll come back to it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Houses and-- and roads and locations and appearances and everything which I remembered was absolutely 100% correct, to the grouting in the house, the way the house was constructed, exactly where the windows were.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "If you would interview me three years ago, I would tell you this is my memory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I don't know how true it is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But now I know it's true because this is the way I verified it.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
